      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "Soient $x_1, x_2, \\dots, x_n > 0$.\nMontrer que $\\frac {x_1}{x_2} + \\frac{x_2}{x_3} + \\dots + \\frac{x_n}{x_1} \\ge n$.",
        "html": "<p>Soient <span class=\"math inline\">\\(x_1, x_2, \\dots, x_n &gt; 0\\)</span>. Montrer que <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\frac {x_1}{x_2} + \\frac{x_2}{x_3} + \\dots + \\frac{x_n}{x_1} \\ge n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "664e47c6-00a2-4683-84c1-72df8d320da4",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$y_i = \\frac{x_i}{x_{i+1}}  \\Rightarrow \n          \\frac n {y_1\\cdots y_n} \\le \\frac{y_1 + \\dots + y_n}n$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\(y_i = \\frac{x_i}{x_{i+1}}  \\Rightarrow \n          \\frac n {y_1\\cdots y_n} \\le \\frac{y_1 + \\dots + y_n}n\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    }
